    651           *
    652           * @note This function is for internal use only.
    653           *
    654           * @note A check to validate that the Power Manager Sleeptimer is expired on
    655           *       top of being the next timer was added. This is because
    656           *       this function is called when coming back from EM2 sleep to validate
    657           *       that the system woke up because of this precise timer expiration.
